# Phase 5: Testing, Deployment, Reporting and Project Completion

## Overview

This phase focuses on testing the Salesforce application, validating all functionalities, generating reports and dashboards, deploying the application for users, and completing the project documentation. The objective is to ensure that the recruitment management system works efficiently and meets the project requirements.

---

## Objectives

- Test all project functionalities.
- Verify data accuracy.
- Generate reports and dashboards.
- Deploy the Salesforce application.
- Prepare final project documentation.
- Demonstrate the working application.

---

## System Testing

The application is tested to ensure that every module functions correctly.

### Test Cases

| Module | Test Description | Expected Result |
|----------|-----------------|-----------------|
| Candidate Registration | Add a new candidate | Candidate record created successfully |
| Job Opening | Create a new job opening | Job opening saved successfully |
| Interview Scheduling | Schedule an interview | Interview record created successfully |
| Candidate Status | Update candidate status | Status updated correctly |
| Reports | Generate recruitment reports | Reports displayed successfully |
| Dashboard | Display recruitment statistics | Dashboard loads correctly |

---

## Testing Summary

The following functionalities were verified:

- Candidate Registration
- Resume Management
- Job Management
- Interview Scheduling
- Candidate Tracking
- Reports Generation
- Dashboard Visualization
- Flow Automation

All modules performed successfully during testing.

---

## Reports

The system generates recruitment reports such as:

- Total Candidates
- Active Job Openings
- Scheduled Interviews
- Selected Candidates
- Rejected Candidates
- Recruitment Status Report

These reports help recruiters monitor recruitment activities efficiently.

---

## Dashboard

Salesforce Dashboards provide visual representation of recruitment data.

Dashboard Components:

- Candidate Distribution
- Job Openings
- Interview Status
- Hiring Progress
- Recruitment Performance

The dashboard enables quick analysis of recruitment activities.

---

## Deployment

The Salesforce application is deployed successfully after testing.

Deployment Activities:

- Final configuration review
- Data validation
- User access verification
- Application deployment
- Final system verification

---

## Project Deliverables

The following deliverables are completed:

- Salesforce Application
- GitHub Repository
- Project Documentation
- Final Project Report
- Presentation (PPT)
- Demo Video

---

## Project Outcome

The AI-Powered Job Recruitment & Candidate Management System provides:

- Automated recruitment workflow
- Centralized candidate management
- Efficient interview scheduling
- Secure data management
- Improved recruiter productivity
- Better hiring decisions

---

## Future Enhancements

Possible future improvements include:

- AI-based candidate ranking
- Resume parsing using Artificial Intelligence
